description: TEHRAN- Iranian President Ebrahim Raisi has emphasized the need to seriously confront any aggression in Iran-Pakistan relations, stating that the border between the two countries is an opportunity for economic exchanges and security enhancement, and must be protected against any insecurity.

description: TEHRAN- The Iranian ambassador to Riyadh, Alireza Enayati, voiced Tehran’s readiness to deepen ties with the Saudi Arabia on scientific, cultural, and religious spheres.

Though Michael O’Flaherty, the director of the bloc’s fundamental rights agency, inaccurately attributed entrenched antisemitic sentiment to a 2023 Hamas operation, his comments prompted reflection on Europe's history of mistreatment towards Jewish people.
